all about yourself, will you?

106
00:14:06,891 --> 00:14:08,800
OK. Stop it about here.

107
00:14:14,190 --> 00:14:18,816
I'm takin' your brake handle
and the reverse key, Denny.

108
00:14:18,944 --> 00:14:20,059
Atchoo!

109
00:14:20,196 --> 00:14:22,651
