in a minute or two.

112
00:14:31,040 --> 00:14:33,957
You will ignore the call.
Is that clear, Mr Doyle?

113
00:14:34,084 --> 00:14:36,622
Yes, sir. They can call
all they want. I'm deaf.

114
00:14:39,423 --> 00:14:42,792
- Thanks, Mr Grey.
- Don't mention it, uh... Mr Green, right?

115
00:14:42,927 --> 00:14:46,545
Right. Let's have your cab key, conductor.

116
00:14:46,680 --> 00:14:49,052
