157
00:17:22,086 --> 00:17:25,003
Well, stopped is better
than backwards at least.

158
00:17:26,298 --> 00:17:29,418
What was that? I didn't know
these things went backwards.

159
00:17:29,552 --> 00:17:31,260
Now you know.

160
00:17:34,807 --> 00:17:38,140
