what you gentlemen are doing?

161
00:17:38,269 --> 00:17:40,308
Yeah, I would.

162
00:18:03,085 --> 00:18:05,541
Come in, Pelham One Two Three.
Come in.

163
00:18:05,671 --> 00:18:08,162
- All right, Mr Green?
- Smooth as silk, Mr Blue.

164
00:18:08,299 --> 00:18:09,959
