- Great.

165
00:18:10,092 --> 00:18:11,421
Get out, Doyle.

166
00:18:11,552 --> 00:18:15,217
Here's your gun. Get going.
We're already two minutes late.

167
00:18:15,347 --> 00:18:18,930
Pelham One Two Three.
Do you hear me, Pelham One Two Three?

168
00:18:22,938 --> 00:18:26,105
Look. The front car's movin'.
And forward this time.

169
00:18:26,233 --> 00:18:29,934
- I've got eyes, haven't I?
- What's goin' on down there?

170
00:18:30,613 --> 00:18:32,652
Are you children with anybody?

171
00:18:32,781 --> 00:18:35,154
You children... you with anybody?

172
00:18:35,284 --> 00:18:37,323
Yeah. My mother.

173
00:18:38,412 --> 00:18:40,120
Go back and join her.

174
00:18:40,247 --> 00:18:43,082
- Why?
- Go back and join your mother.

175
