Mom, we wanna play.

176
00:19:07,691 --> 00:19:09,649
Your attention, please.

177
00:19:11,654 --> 00:19:16,612
You'll all remain seated. Anybody
who tries to rise is going to get shot.

178
00:19:21,205 --> 00:19:23,197
There's another one!

179
00:19:23,332 --> 00:19:25,040
Shut up!

180
00:19:25,167 --> 00:19:27,207
Move up a bit, Mr Doyle.

181
00:19:28,754 --> 00:19:31,079
Ladies and gentlemen, you see this gun?

182
