- Let her sleep.

209
00:21:34,421 --> 00:21:37,209
What you're going to do, Mr Doyle,
is to go back,

210
00:21:37,341 --> 00:21:40,675
collect all the passengers
from the cars we've cut loose,

211
00:21:40,803 --> 00:21:43,970
and walk them to 28th Street station.

212
00:21:44,098 --> 00:21:47,633
