229
00:23:09,016 --> 00:23:10,676
All right, Mr Green?

230
00:23:10,809 --> 00:23:13,645
The power's off at 14th Street and 33rd.

231
00:23:13,771 --> 00:23:17,982
All four tracks. Local and express.

232
00:23:18,108 --> 00:23:20,231
The north and the southbound.

233
00:23:20,361 --> 00:23:22,187
